      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_4719150569776066802.png",
                "id": "talent21065",
                "key": "Yunlai Swordsmanship",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Yunlai Swordsmanship"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Lightning Stiletto</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/855f8d96be42fe05d7f7d66b60fad1a6_6366848529116509629.png",
                "id": "talent35296",
                "key": "Stellar Restoration",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Stellar Restoration"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\"> Electro DMG</span>, deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/9950bc530ec62d8e01daf47fe1229216_6996121677534947275.png",
                "id": "talent27089",
                "key": "Starward Sword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Starward Sword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Lightning Stiletto</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Event Card</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Combat Actions</span>: Switch your Keqing in to be the active character and immediately use Stellar Restoration once. This instance of Stellar Restoration will grant Keqing <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Infusion</span> without creating another Lightning Stiletto. (When Keqing uses Stellar Restoration with this card in Hand: Instead of creating another Lightning Stiletto, discard this card and Keqing gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Infusion</span>)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Electro Infusion</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>The character to which this is attached has their Physical DMG dealt converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1840725084548997174.png",
                "id": "talent34599",
                "key": "Lightning Stiletto",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/d6793b3314d1b255f49f2ba1ec500b38_7315783418333362182.png",
                "title": "Lightning Stiletto"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_4828322067096551325.png",
                "id": "talent60261",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bounses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Combat Action</span></strong></p><p>After you finish 1 Combat Action, it will be your opponents turn.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Playing a card from your Hand with this rule is also a Combat Action rather than a Fast Action.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_496952867129860645.png",
                "id": "talent54913",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
